Checking git after a crash
Aggregation kind of working...
Aggregation kind of working but other things not working...
Added tests for ComparitorLocation and DifferenceLocation
Added tests for Aggregater
Fixed a bug screwing up GvComment when used as a key in GvDataMap. Caused by GvCommentList setting first entries as headlines.

In the process of fixing tests that don't work in light of recent changes.
Added a GvCOmmentHandler to FactoryGvDataHandler to handle the seeting of headlines when no data etc.
Fixed some of the dialog tests
Fixed Dialog tests
Fixed all tests
Typed the GridDataViewers, ReviewViewAdapters and GridCellExpanders
Typed the GridDataViewers, ReviewViewAdapters and GridCellExpanders. Adjusted tests accordingly.
Simplified ReviewAdapterModel by simplifying some classes and removing some others. Adjusted tests accordingly. Added tests for TagCollector and ViewerGvDataMap.
Added another test review

better separated ReviewFeed from FeedScreen.
Added ReviewChildListScreen to abstract main functionality from FeedScreen
Added ReviewsManager to find reviews based on id
Adjusted tests in light of recent changes

Fixed bug in VhReviewOverview that wasn't emptying comment view if no comment
Fixed bug where GvDataMap wasn't valid for display if no items.
Changed ViewHolderAdapter to return new View if data not valid for display.
Simplified GvDataList so as not to need data class.
Added GvCanonical and GvCanonicalList to take place of GvDataMap for aggregation
djusted tests in light of recent changes
